room_title: Escape room "Time Paradox" by Amazing Escape Room in Freehold
room_description: As students of a professor of temporal anomalies, you’ve stumbled upon a time machine back to the past.  Use your brains to outwit the professor’s contraptions and make your way back to the present. Take too long and you may just run into yourselves, creating a time paradox that will unravel the entirety of the space-time continuum!
